title: Rabbit™ Wine-Aerating Pourer by Metrokane
description:
We love this aerator for how easy it makes bringing delicious flavors out of your wine. Insert pourer in bottleneck and pour through to aerate red wine as you serve your guests. 

The product featured can be purchased at: http://www.surlatable.com/product/PRO-672170/Rabbit-Wine-Aerating-Pourer-by-Metrokane
